text.textblock: Take notice that Commission staff will meet with representatives of Overland Trail Transmission Company in an informal, pre-filing conference to discuss Overland Trail's petition for rate approval under ยง284.123(b)(2) of the Commission's regulations which must be filed no later than March 31, 1994. The conference will be held on Wednesday, February 9, 1994, at 10 a.m. in a room to be designated at the offices of the Federal Energy Regulatory Commission, 825 North Capitol Street, NE., Washington, DC 20426.
Attendance will be open to any interested party. For additional information, please contact Mark Hegerle at (202) 208-0927.
